Cell.Data: This spreadsheet supports the exchange of building, system and product information through the life of the project.
Individual worksheets are organized by project phase as shown below
Sets of spaces sharing a specific attribute
Types of equipment, products, and materials
Sets of components providing a service
Constituents for Types, Components and others
Economic, Environmental and Social Impacts at various stages in the life cycle
Note: submittals and approvals added on Documents
Note: manufacturer and model added on Type
Note: serial and tag added on Component
PM, Safety, and other job plans
Note: warranty information added on Type
Spatial locations in box, line, or point format
reference to other sheet or pick list
secondary information when preparing product data
Note: Regional, owner, or product specific data may be added as new columns to the right of standard template columns.
Note: Regional classification codes may be substituted for the specifiable picklists used in the United States.
